This paper is primarily focused on privacy and security concerns related to smartphone apps, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of crowdsourcing and in situ traffic analysis, which are related to social and information retrieval (cs.SI) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), respectively. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of cryptographic hashing, which is related to cryptography (cs.CY) and network security (cs.NI).
